name: Sunny Private Room in Chestnut hill
description:
Sunny private room in a two bed one bath apartment complex. All of the conveniences of what Boston has to offer, but tucked in a quiet neighborhood with beautiful lake and plenty of green fields. The location is: Fun, Convenient, Quiet, Inexpensive, & Clean. We have fresh, new linens for the queen sized bed. This is a great place for group travel (2 people max), a quiet business trip, or any kind of private getaway. This truly is a great place to stay.

The space
-Overview
This is a 2 bedroom apartment, one full bath, one living room, one kitchen, one free private parking space, shared laundry, and a public swimming pool (summer hours only). This is everything you could ever want for a fun trip, a business stay, or a longer visit to the area. There are hardwood floors throughout the unit and it is meticulously cleaned.

name: Beautiful Private Two Bedroom Apt in Boston
description:
Cozy Beautiful Two bedroom Apt in Boston. All of the conveniences of what Boston has to offer, but tucked in a quiet neighborhood with beautiful lake and plenty of green fields. The location is: Fun, Convenient, Quiet, Inexpensive, & Clean. We have fresh, new linens for the queen sized bed. This is a great place for group travel (4 people max), a quiet business trip, or any kind of private getaway. This truly is a great place to stay.

The space
Highlights
Private entire apt for group travellers or vacation seekers in a quiet section of the Chestnut hill neighborhood of Boston. Includes two new queen size beds, free wi-fi, fan, new closet for clothing, desk/chair and use of the kitchen and bathroom. There is also a private outdoor pool accessible by only residents in this apartment.
